{"type":"message","id":"70d3cd17","parentId":"12dbc30c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T20:20:26.302Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01HDPKk8eWkVfScqr6Pu7Fvo","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<Modal v-model=\"showStepSelector\" title=\"选择步骤\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n        <button\n          v-for=\"n in 12\"\n          :key=\"n\"\n          class=\"p-3 rounded-lg border-2 text-left transition-colors\"\n          :class=\"{\n            'border-primary-500 bg-primary-50': n === currentStep,\n            'border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300': n !== currentStep\n          }\"\n          @click=\"navigateToStep(n)\"\n        >\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">步骤 {{ n }}</span>\n            <Icon\n              v-if=\"formStore.isStepCompleted(n)\"\n              name=\"mdi:check-circle\"\n              class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500\"\n            />\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">{{ getStepTitle(n) }}</span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </Modal>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nconst formStore = useFormStore()\nconst router = useRouter()\n\nconst currentStep = computed(() => formStore.currentStep)\nconst showStepSelector = ref(false)\n\nconst goToPreviousStep = () => {\n  if (currentStep.value > 1) {\n    navigateToStep(currentStep.value - 1)\n  }\n}\n\nconst goToNextStep = () => {\n  if (currentStep.value < 12) {\n    navigateToStep(currentStep.value + 1)\n  }\n}\n\nconst navigateToStep = (step: number) => {\n  formStore.setCurrentStep(step)\n  router.push(`/app/form/step-${step}`)\n  showStepSelector.value = false\n}\n\nconst getStepTitle = (step: number): string => {\n  const titles: Record<number, string> = {\n    1: '个人信息',\n    2: '护照信息',\n    3: '联系方式',\n    4: '旅行信息',\n    5: '旅行伙伴',\n    6: '美国联系人',\n    7: '家庭信息',\n    8: '工作/教育',\n    9: '安全问题(1)',\n    10: '安全问题(2)',\n    11: '以往旅行',\n    12: '照片与确认'\n  }\n  return titles[step] || ''\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n由于输出长度限制，我需要继续在下一个回复中完成剩余的组件和stores。\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNext speaker: User\n\n\n================================================================================\n✅ 开发流程完成！\n================================================================================\n\n================================================================================\n📤 推送代码到GitHub...\n================================================================================\n$ git init\n$ git add .\n$ git commit -m \"Initial commit: DS-160 Helper MVP by AG2 Team\"\n⚠️  命令执行警告: \n$ git branch -M main\n$ git remote add origin https://ruoqianfengshao:***TOKEN***@github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\n$ git push -u origin main --force\n⚠️  命令执行警告: error: src refspec main does not match any\nerror: failed to push some refs to 'https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git'\n\n\n✅ 代码已推送到GitHub!\n🔗 查看仓库: https://github.com/ruoqianfengshao/ds-160.git\n================================================================================"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"<Modal v-model=\"showStepSelector\" title=\"选择步骤\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n        <button\n          v-for=\"n in 12\"\n          :key=\"n\"\n          class=\"p-3 rounded-lg border-2 text-left transition-colors\"\n          :class=\"{\n            'border-primary-500 bg-primary-50': n === currentStep,\n            'border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300': n !== currentStep\n          }\"\n          @click=\"navigateToStep(n)\"\n        >\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">步骤 {{ n }}</span>\n            <Icon\n              v-if=\"formStore.isStepCompleted(n)\"\n              name=\"mdi:check-circle\"\n              class=\"w